{"tid":2493484,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歐陽震華唔識友台：只諗到亞視","createTime":"2021-04-18T03:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T06:55:26.000Z","uid":212249,"like":9,"dislike":307,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"13e912e845c3944772470e9091a705beee74dd27","tid":2493484,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:09:46.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】陳瀅、歐陽震華、馬德鐘等昨日宣傳劇集《伙記辦大事》，陳瀅扮演學生妹成為話題，她拒絕再演並提議監製找人扮演自己的後生版，好姊妹賴慰玲及蔡思貝睇過都有微言。另一幕被男友傷害激動到涕淚交下，她稱與初戀經歷相似，被追問下自爆只有4段感情，身邊朋友都急於介紹對象，但她拒絕「相睇」，笑言覺得尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n而觀眾期待歐陽震華與馬德鐘正式鬥戲帶起收視，提到友台聲勢勁，身為「收視福將」會否有壓力？歐陽震華稱：「友台？邊度？（ViuTV？）我仲停留在80年代，只想到ATV，大家不要枷鎖我，福將都要看表現，馬德鐘也是視帝，並不是大家說他是就是，但現在更是男神啦！」"},{"pid":"7df298c80b90b57f99aa5934b9d9f6a7b76efe12","tid":2493484,"uid":212249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E9%9C%87%E8%8F%AF%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%E5%8F%8B%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8F%AA%E8%AB%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%9E%E8%A6%96-223000188.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AD%2590%25E9%2599%25BD%25E9%259C%2587%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%2594%2594%25E8%25AD%2598%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E5%258F%25AA%25E8%25AB%2597%25E5%2588%25B0%25E4%25BA%259E%25E8%25A6%2596-223000188.html&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=ebfdeb61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E9%99%BD%E9%9C%87%E8%8F%AF%E5%94%94%E8%AD%98%E5%8F%8B%E5%8F%B0-%E5%8F%AA%E8%AB%97%E5%88%B0%E4%BA%9E%E8%A6%96-223000188.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb0d739a6f7a8d02699a8137bf400e58b1b47f13","tid":2493484,"uid":23707,"like":297,"dislike":1,"score":296,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:10:52.000Z","msg":"80年代？即係留戀英殖時代？"},{"pid":"26b6699d2c2944d9c52a8ed754d727dd75c7309b","tid":2493484,"uid":23170,"like":154,"dislike":1,"score":153,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T03:11:07.000Z","msg":"歐陽震華段嘢一半書面一半口語，佢講嘢咁撚奇怪嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 